title: Washtenaw County Board of Commissioners Districts
name: Washtenaw County Board of Commissioners Districts
description: This feature class displays the Washtenaw County Board of Commissioner Districts.  These boundaries are based off the results of the 2000 census, but were not put into effect until January 1, 2003.  The boundaries were digitized based off the "Washtenaw County, Michigan - Adopted Washtenaw County Commissioner District Apportionment Plan," which was written by the Washtenaw County Apportionment Commistion, and submitted June 8, 2001.
